WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.330 --> 00:00:07.964
We'll start with some simple stats,

00:00:07.964 --> 00:00:11.175
to tell us how Sparkify customers use our service.

00:00:11.175 --> 00:00:14.730
Let's begin with the daily listening time, for an average user.

00:00:14.730 --> 00:00:16.740
In other words, how long is

00:00:16.739 --> 00:00:20.534
the average Sparkify user actually listening to music per day.

00:00:20.535 --> 00:00:24.240
After that, we'll calculate the number of songs per day,

00:00:24.239 --> 00:00:28.479
including any repeat or partial listens, for the average user.

